text: The Romanian Orthodox Diocese of Hungary (Hungarian: Magyarországi Román Ortodox Egyházmegye or Gyulai Román Ortodox Püspökség; Romanian: Episcopia Ortodoxă Română din Ungaria) is the part of the Romanian Orthodox Church, the bishopric of the orthodox romanians in Hungary. ==References== Category:Eastern Orthodox Church Category:Romanian culture
title: Romanian Orthodox Diocese of Hungary
